race.comment: A good race. RHOOKY (4) returns after six months in the paddock. Closed the last campaign with a 3L defeat over 2000m at Flemington in stronger and it was a big effort after settling back. He went close over 1700m at Warrnambool on debut prior. Has had three jumpouts and Bates stays aboard from the Flemington run. Will have come on and will be tough to beat. NEVERENOUGHLEGO (6) has put together back-to-back placings, the latest when 1.3 lengths away over 1400m at Wangaratta. Ready for the mile and it's hard to risk the Hayes yard. MAKHANDA (3) was prominent at the bend and just missed over 1600m at Echuca. He has more to offer and should be in the finish. BONCAPO (5) was beaten 0.8L over 1400m at Horsham on debut. He should enjoy the step up to the mile and maps well. In the premier stable and is sure to keep improving.
